These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip, orchid, daffodil, marigold, rose, balloon-flower
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who growslily is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 2. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Flower   | daffodil | lily | balloon-flower | tulip    | orchid | marigold   | rose    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

