.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, martial-arts, sports, scientific, comedy, disaster
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific | martial-arts | comedy | zombie | disaster | satire      | sports  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

