.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie, satire, action, crime, superhero, disaster
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, hamster, pony, rabbit, rat, turtle
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person watching action movies is the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the turtle and the person watching action movies##2
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | crime | time-travel | zombie   | action | satire | superhero |
| Pet           | rabbit | rat     | goat     | hamster | pony   | fish   | turtle    |

