.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, light-blue, azure, lilac, amber, blood-red, brown
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 6. the mexican is between the person who likes azure and the pakistani##2
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Color      | azure    | amber  | lilac  | fuchsia  | brown      | blood-red       | light-blue |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

