.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, poker, billiard, whist, go, scrabble
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing monopoly##2
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing billiard##1
9. the person playing whist is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Game   | billiard      | whist | monopoly | poker | scrabble      | canasta      | go |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

