 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the person drinking cola##2
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
