 3. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes grey and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 7. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person who likes white is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Beverage      | 7up   | fanta | almond-milk | sprite | mirinda | tea   | iced-tea |
